OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA mainly dry and partly cloudy
OL,6,Fmorning. Sunny spells will develop
OL,7,Fduring the day alongside a few
OL,8,Fshowers, some of which may be on the
OL,9,Fheavy side.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FShowers will die out this
OL,12,Fevening. Then turning cloudier with
OL,13,Frain spreading in from the west during
OL,14,Fthe early hours, this occasionally
OL,15,Fheavy later. Freshening winds for
OL,16,FArgyll.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
