OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CTuesday:FA cloudy morning with
OL,6,Foccasional heavy rain at first.
OL,7,FShowers will develop for the
OL,8,Fafternoon, some possibly heavy with
OL,9,Fthe odd rumble of thunder. Argyll
OL,10,Frather windy.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:
OL,13,FVariable amounts of cloud with showers
OL,14,For a few spells of rain, some of which
OL,15,Fmay be on the heavy side. Often rather
OL,16,Fwarm in any sunny spells.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
